OL,3,CMan jailed after strangling partner to
OL,4,Cdeath and 'showing no remorse'
OL,6,FA man who strangled his partner to
OL,7,Fdeath after drinking heavily and
OL,8,Ftaking cocaine has been sentenced to
OL,9,Flife behind bars.
OL,11,FAlcwyn Thomas killed the mother of
OL,12,Ftwo, Victoria 'Vicki' Thomas, in
OL,13,FAugust 2024, claiming it was a "sex
OL,14,Fgame gone wrong".
OL,16,FCardiff Crown Court heard that
OL,17,FVictoria's body was found during the
OL,18,Fearly hours of Tuesday 20 August after
OL,19,Fa family member went to check on her
OL,20,Fwelfare.
