OL,6,FMs Thomas had died having sustained
OL,7,Fpressure to her neck.
OL,9,FThe court saw CCTV from the night of
OL,10,Fthe murder, which showed 44-year-old
OL,11,FAlcwyn Thomas and Vicki Thomas, 45,
OL,12,Fleaving Club 3000 bingo in Gabalfa,
OL,13,FCardiff. The footage shows the couple
OL,14,Fappearing to argue with each other
OL,15,Fwhile waiting for a taxi.
OL,17,FPolice later discovered Thomas had
OL,18,Ftaken cocaine and drunk 16 pints of
OL,19,Flager.
