OL,4,Cdeath and 'showing no remorse'
OL,6,FThe court heard how Ms Thomas was
OL,7,Ffound dead by police wearing her
OL,8,Fdressing gown, after Alcwyn Thomas'
OL,9,Fniece had gone to the house in
OL,10,FBirchgrove, Cardiff, to check on her.
OL,11,FA post-mortem found she had been
OL,12,Fstrangled to death.
OL,14,FProsecutor Michael Jones KC added that
OL,15,Fwhen police arrived: "The defendant
OL,16,Fwas found in the bedroom on the middle
OL,17,Ffloor, having, he said, taken an
OL,18,Fapparent overdose. He was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
