OL,3,CMan jailed after strangling partner to
OL,4,Cdeath and 'showing no remorse'
OL,6,F"He maintained it was sex gone wrong
OL,7,Fand that it was during, to use his
OL,8,Fwords, 'erotic asphyxiation' that she
OL,9,Fhad died."
OL,11,FSentencing him to a minimum of 20
OL,12,Fyears, the judge said: "Your lack of
OL,13,Fremorse was notable. At no time did
OL,14,Fyou express sorrow or remorse for your
OL,15,Factions, even though you admitted
OL,16,Fkilling Ms Thomas."
