OL,6,FVicki's two sons read impact
OL,7,Fstatements to the Church. Cole
OL,8,FCrossfield, Ms Thomas' eldest son,
OL,9,Fsaid: "I write this victim's personal
OL,10,Fstatement following the murder of my
OL,11,Famazing mum, Victoria Thomas.
OL,13,F"She was my best friend. Our
OL,14,Fconnection is beyond the words and
OL,15,Ftime I have today.
OL,17,F"The disgusting method he chose to
OL,18,Ftake my mother's life has left images
OL,19,Fin my head that will never leave me...
OL,20,FThere are a plethora of other images
OL,21,Fand scenes I find unbearable.
