OL,6,F"My mum was my best friend and our
OL,7,Fconnection was unbreakable."
OL,9,FHer younger son, Shay Crossfield,
OL,10,Fsaid: "I stand here today less than a
OL,11,Fmonth after my 18th birthday, a
OL,12,Fmilestone birthday, one with an
OL,13,Foverwhelming feeling of loss, the loss
OL,14,Fof my beloved mum.
OL,16,F"I passed my driving test the day
OL,17,Fbefore her funeral, and I never got to
OL,18,Fshow her that blue certificate.
