OL,6,F"(Alcywn Thomas) brutally took my
OL,7,Fmother's life last year. Every day,
OL,8,Ffor every second, of every minute, I
OL,9,Fwill have to live with the loss of my
OL,10,Fmother. We will never know the true
OL,11,Fstory of how she lost her life.
OL,13,F"She will not be with me for the rest
